title: Killing the Fitness Queen
description: Amateur psychic sleuth Natalie Miller is back in an exciting new adventure!After taking a new job with Hollywood actor Simon Bellamy, psychic detective Natalie Miller returns to her home town of Treeville from a whirl wind six month adventure. All she wants to do is rest and relax, however BFF Karen has other ideas. After convincing her to do some minor psychic work, Karen gets Natalie involved in the high profile murder case of a fitness guru, working for the defendant’s sister, who just happens to be Natalie's ex-husband's wife! Read along as Natalie navigates through uncharted territory, which tests her skills as a psychic and friend. She discovers the hard way that people change and friendships don’t always equal loyalty.
author: Ella Meeks
